@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "User" as AUser

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Camera Viewer UI" as UI
  control "Favorites Controller" as FC
  entity "Favorite" as FavoriteEntity
  entity "User" as UserEntity
  entity "Camera" as CameraEntity
}

AUser --> UI : click "Add to Favorites"
UI --> FC : add favorite request
FC --> UserEntity : identify user
FC --> CameraEntity : fetch selected camera
FC --> FavoriteEntity : create Favorite\n(user + camera)
FC --> UI : confirm added

note bottom of UI
After logging in, a favorites button appears.
Users can add cameras to their favorites list.
end note
@enduml